{"tid":2409493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連韓團BTS都入圍到今年GRAMMY獎，是否該反思一下點解華語歌手仍然無一個可以入圍？","createTime":"2021-02-16T00:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T02:37:38.000Z","uid":100680,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aea0426c2a506c06f48c428c52ff468827493cac","tid":2409493,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"GRAMMY獎係全世界公認含金量最高的音樂頒獎禮<br />\n歐美不論各流派系音樂人莫講話可以得到一座獎項，甚至只要能夠成功入圍就已經算係對自己的最大肯定<br />\n<br />\n2020年11月GRAMMY公佈入圍名單<br />\n其中＂最佳流行樂歌手獎＂<br />\n<br />\nJ Balvin, Dua Lipa, Bad Bunny and Tainy - Un Dia (One Day)<br />\nJustin Bieber featuring Quavo - Intentions<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>BTS - Dynamite</strong></span><br />\nLady Gaga and Ariana Grande - Rain on Me<br />\nTaylor Swift featuring Bon Iver - Exile<br />\n<br />\n繼日本的喜多朗，B'z之後<br />\n第三名可以入圍GRAMMY獎的亞洲人 - 韓國的BTS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，已經發展左差唔多40年的華語樂壇係唔係應該反思一下<br />\n明明韓國樂壇比起華語樂壇算係遲左起步，點解韓國終於有人可以入圍到GRAMMY獎<br />\n而華語樂壇仍然仲未有人可以入圍到？更莫講話可以得獎<br />\n<br />\n我仍然記得周杰倫分別在2003年同2009年兩度公開講過<br />\n佢畢生最大心願就係要成為第一位可以入圍GRAMMY的華人歌手<br />\n但而家佢......"},{"pid":"9eb9b1725000a189e5fd1be2be2272099c2994c5","tid":2409493,"uid":53421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:39:29.000Z","msg":"放心 下次到mirror"},{"pid":"a72206ef3371b5ed0885b3f3be363305be2f2baa","tid":2409493,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾KPOP出D英文歌先入到😑"},{"pid":"a5b8a365757120ad2eca7b37a150f1f10b4417f2","tid":2409493,"uid":100680,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a72206ef3371b5ed0885b3f3be363305be2f2baa","tid":2409493,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾KPOP出D英文歌先入到😑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:56:35.000Z","msg":"人地grammy係評審制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算出英文歌都要睇你首歌係唔係真係高水準先俾你入圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji